1. Moram da zakažem *tretman* za masažu. (I need to schedule a *treatment* for a massage.)
2. Naša klinika nudi različite vrste *tretmana* za kožu lica. (Our clinic offers various types of *treatments* for facial skin.)
3. Lekar je propisao *tretman* antibioticima. (The doctor prescribed a *treatment* with antibiotics.)
4. Klijenti su bili veoma zadovoljni *tretmanom* koji smo im pružili. (The clients were very satisfied with the *treatment* we provided them.)
5. Ne bi trebalo da *tretirate* svoje kolege na takav način. (You shouldn't *treat* your colleagues in that way.)
6. Naša firma *tretira* svoje zaposlene s poštovanjem. (Our company *treats* its employees with respect.)
7. Da bi se sprečila pojava bolesti, neophodno je redovno *tretirati* prostorije. (To prevent the spread of disease, it is necessary to regularly *treat* the premises.)